<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-25-0332 </DOCNO><TEXT>The SEARS Model is a comprehensive, highly flexible, user-oriented systemfor projecting economic, demographic, public service and fiscal impactsof a high-level nuclear waste repository siting. Both baseline and project-relatedimpact projections may be performed for regions, counties, municipalities,and school districts. It is an interactive APL model requiring comprehensivedata bases and parameters to generate the outputs desired. 75 refs.,24 figs., 14 tabs.</TEXT></DOC>